Hello! My name is Alex, and I am with RT 6 Boozers. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex! I have a question about your happy hour specials.

Of course! I’d be happy to help with that. May I start by getting your name?

Sure, my name is Jamie.

Great to meet you, Jamie! To provide you with the best information, could you please share your email address?

That sounds great! I look forward to visiting RT 6 Boozers soon.

Thank you for your time, Jamie! We look forward to serving you at RT 6 Boozers. Have a wonderful day!
